1. *Carl* je kupio novi automobil. (Carl bought a new car.)
2. Moja sestra se udala za *Carla*. (My sister married Carl.)
3. *Carl* je poslao pismo direktoru. (Carl sent a letter to the director.)
4. Deca vole da se igraju sa *Carlovim* psom. (Children love to play with Carl's dog.)
5. *Carl* je bio veoma ljut kada je saznao istinu. (Carl was very angry when he found out the truth.)
6. *Carlu* se dopada da čita knjige. (Carl likes to read books.)
7. *Carl* je bio veoma uspešan na poslu. (Carl was very successful at work.)
8. *Carla* nisam video već godinu dana. (I haven't seen Carl for a year.)
9. *Carl* je zaboravio da zatvori prozor. (Carl forgot to close the window.)
10. *Carl* je bio predivan domaćin tokom naše posete. (Carl was a wonderful host during our visit.)